Text.SourceString: Darling, this wrap isn't just fabric, it's history dancing around your shoulders. See...see?
Text.LocalizedString: Darling, this wrap isn't just fabric, it's history dancing around your shoulders. See...see?

Text.SourceString: Oh, honey, touch this! Made from the silkiest sand fibers—yes, from the land!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, honey, touch this! Made from the silkiest sand fibers—yes, from the land!

Text.SourceString: Only the most skilled hands can weave this magic.//<portrait=happy>It’s like wearing a cloud, if clouds were underwater.
Text.LocalizedString: Only the most skilled hands can weave this magic.//<portrait=happy>It’s like wearing a cloud, if clouds were underwater.

Text.SourceString: You must see this, sweetie! Bioluminescent trim is all the rave now. It's like wearing the stars around your chest.
Text.LocalizedString: You must see this, sweetie! Bioluminescent trim is all the rave now. It's like wearing the stars around your chest.

Text.SourceString: Who wouldn’t want to sparkle like a night sky?
Text.LocalizedString: Who wouldn’t want to sparkle like a night sky?

Text.SourceString: Listen here, a little insider tip—rinse these gems in moonlit seawater. It keeps them dazzling, and darling, we all deserve to dazzle!
Text.LocalizedString: Listen here, a little insider tip—rinse these gems in moonlit seawater. It keeps them dazzling, and darling, we all deserve to dazzle!

Text.SourceString: This fabulous top? As eco-friendly as it gets. Made from recycled sea glass threads—nothing but the best, because we care, darling, we really do!
Text.LocalizedString: This fabulous top? As eco-friendly as it gets. Made from recycled sea glass threads—nothing but the best, because we care, darling, we really do!

Text.SourceString: Oh, darling, have you heard? Slamet’s mermoos went on a little adventure the other day—straight into my display and <NPCName>Galoong</>'s!//<portrait=happy>Caused quite the splash, literally!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, darling, have you heard? Slamet’s mermoos went on a little adventure the other day—straight into my display and <NPCName>Galoong</>'s!//<portrait=happy>Caused quite the splash, literally!

Text.SourceString: And now, the word around is that one cheeky mermoo might still be hiding in <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>’s house.//Can you imagine finding a mer-moo in your bed? The nerve!
Text.LocalizedString: And now, the word around is that one cheeky mermoo might still be hiding in <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>’s house.//Can you imagine finding a mer-moo in your bed? The nerve!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Jannu</>—bless his heart—had to show a customer the door the other night.//<portrait=happy>Apparently, they'd had a bit too much deep sea elixir and started serenading a group of startled sea cucumbers with what they claimed was 'ancient merfolk opera.'
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Jannu</>—bless his heart—had to show a customer the door the other night.//<portrait=happy>Apparently, they'd had a bit too much deep sea elixir and started serenading a group of startled sea cucumbers with what they claimed was 'ancient merfolk opera.'

Text.SourceString: The sea cucumbers weren’t impressed, and neither was <NPCName>Jannu</>!
Text.LocalizedString: The sea cucumbers weren’t impressed, and neither was <NPCName>Jannu</>!

Text.SourceString: Oh, <NPCName>Jannu</>, it’s no secret he's as single as a clam.//Trust me, he's not just playing hard to get—he truly hasn't shown a flicker of interest in other fish or...well, anyone really. I should know.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <NPCName>Jannu</>, it’s no secret he's as single as a clam.//Trust me, he's not just playing hard to get—he truly hasn't shown a flicker of interest in other fish or...well, anyone really. I should know.

Text.SourceString: I keep telling <NPCName>Jannu</>, 'You won't find love hiding behind those coral stacks!'//<portrait=happy>But you know <NPCName>Jannu</>, always focused on his next big deal.
Text.LocalizedString: I keep telling <NPCName>Jannu</>, 'You won't find love hiding behind those coral stacks!'//<portrait=happy>But you know <NPCName>Jannu</>, always focused on his next big deal.

Text.SourceString: Oh, a dear cutie came by yesterday, looking for something to match his sparkling personality.//I told him, 'Honey, with a glow like yours, you could light up the darkest depths of the ocean! You're the real gem here.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, a dear cutie came by yesterday, looking for something to match his sparkling personality.//I told him, 'Honey, with a glow like yours, you could light up the darkest depths of the ocean! You're the real gem here.

Text.SourceString: My friend from the North Sea gave me a hat that floats on water!//<portrait=annoyed>Can you imagine? A floating hat! What will they think of next, floating belts?
Text.LocalizedString: My friend from the North Sea gave me a hat that floats on water!//<portrait=annoyed>Can you imagine? A floating hat! What will they think of next, floating belts?

Text.SourceString: A trader from the surface once brought me a scarf that could stay afloat!//<portrait=normal>Can you believe it? A floating scarf! Those land dwellers always come up with the most surprising things.
Text.LocalizedString: A trader from the surface once brought me a scarf that could stay afloat!//<portrait=normal>Can you believe it? A floating scarf! Those land dwellers always come up with the most surprising things.

Text.SourceString: I must say, her clothes were quite interesting—they almost made her look like one of us.//But don't be fooled, she's definitely a land dweller. Her name’s <NPCName>Ratih</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I must say, her clothes were quite interesting—they almost made her look like one of us.//But don't be fooled, she's definitely a land dweller. Her name’s <NPCName>Ratih</>.

Text.SourceString: If you ever feel adventurous, sprinkle a bit of crushed pepper on your seaweed flakes.//It’s zesty, it’s tangy...spice!
Text.LocalizedString: If you ever feel adventurous, sprinkle a bit of crushed pepper on your seaweed flakes.//It’s zesty, it’s tangy...spice!

Text.SourceString: Always, and I mean always, lead with your best fin forward.//Whether it's the freshest fish or the sparkliest skirt, start strong, my dear!
Text.LocalizedString: Always, and I mean always, lead with your best fin forward.//Whether it's the freshest fish or the sparkliest skirt, start strong, my dear!

Text.SourceString: We’re all about saving our seas, sweetheart. Every thread in this shop is chosen to ensure our oceans stay as pristine as they are pretty.
Text.LocalizedString: We’re all about saving our seas, sweetheart. Every thread in this shop is chosen to ensure our oceans stay as pristine as they are pretty.

Text.SourceString: Welcome, welcome! Don’t be shy, check this out!
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome, welcome! Don’t be shy, check this out!

Text.SourceString: Hello, my sparkling friend! Ready to add some shimmer to your wardrobe today?
Text.LocalizedString: Hello, my sparkling friend! Ready to add some shimmer to your wardrobe today?

Text.SourceString: Oh, what a delight to see you!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, what a delight to see you!

Text.SourceString: Welcome! I can tell you’re about to brighten my day!
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome! I can tell you’re about to brighten my day!

Text.SourceString: Greetings, sea-star! Caught any good currents on your way here?//Let’s catch you some compliments next!
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, sea-star! Caught any good currents on your way here?//Let’s catch you some compliments next!

Text.SourceString: Hey! Fancy seeing you here! Let’s find you the perfect outfit to match that dazzling smile.
Text.LocalizedString: Hey! Fancy seeing you here! Let’s find you the perfect outfit to match that dazzling smile.

Text.SourceString: Look who’s swimming by! Always a pleasure to see a familiar fin.
Text.LocalizedString: Look who’s swimming by! Always a pleasure to see a familiar fin.

Text.SourceString: Welcome, welcome! Don’t be shy, check this out!
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome, welcome! Don’t be shy, check this out!

Text.SourceString: Can you imagine, walking on two legs all day? Well, you can, I guess. My gosh...
Text.LocalizedString: Can you imagine, walking on two legs all day? Well, you can, I guess. My gosh...

Text.SourceString: Ah, shoes! You put them on to walk around so you don't hurt your feet.//<portrait=concerned>But then, why not just grow tougher feet? Seems like a lot of extra work.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, shoes! You put them on to walk around so you don't hurt your feet.//<portrait=concerned>But then, why not just grow tougher feet? Seems like a lot of extra work.

Text.SourceString: You drink water without filtering it through gills up there? Straight up? Bold choice.
Text.LocalizedString: You drink water without filtering it through gills up there? Straight up? Bold choice.

Text.SourceString: So, you humans have something called 'electricity,' right? It’s like magic but with wires.//Oh yeah, I know everything about electricity.
Text.LocalizedString: So, you humans have something called 'electricity,' right? It’s like magic but with wires.//Oh yeah, I know everything about electricity.

Text.SourceString: Live on land? Oh, honey, I'd miss the sway of the sea too much.
Text.LocalizedString: Live on land? Oh, honey, I'd miss the sway of the sea too much.

Text.SourceString: Imagine me, living among trees instead of coral? I'd feel like a fish out of water—literally!
Text.LocalizedString: Imagine me, living among trees instead of coral? I'd feel like a fish out of water—literally!

Text.SourceString: Ah, taxes! Yes, we pay them here too—gotta keep our coral palaces and kelp gardens flourishing.//Even underwater, the taxman swims.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, taxes! Yes, we pay them here too—gotta keep our coral palaces and kelp gardens flourishing.//Even underwater, the taxman swims.

Text.SourceString: Every shell counts when it comes to kingdom dues. It’s our way of keeping the currents clean and the sea-police happy.//Can't have the anemones complaining, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Every shell counts when it comes to kingdom dues. It’s our way of keeping the currents clean and the sea-police happy.//Can't have the anemones complaining, right?

Text.SourceString: If you're looking to spruce up your grotto, <NPCName>Galoong</>'s your merman.//Now, I have no favorites, but let's just say his decor is a bit more...polished than his partner <NPCName>Vihren</>'s.
Text.LocalizedString: If you're looking to spruce up your grotto, <NPCName>Galoong</>'s your merman.//Now, I have no favorites, but let's just say his decor is a bit more...polished than his partner <NPCName>Vihren</>'s.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Galoong</>, oh, he's a wizard with his hands.//Turns a simple sea rock into a masterpiece.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Galoong</>, oh, he's a wizard with his hands.//Turns a simple sea rock into a masterpiece.

Text.SourceString: Now, don’t go spending all your coins at Galoong's shop over there.//Save some for a fabulous new outfit, honey. Trust me, you need it.
Text.LocalizedString: Now, don’t go spending all your coins at Galoong's shop over there.//Save some for a fabulous new outfit, honey. Trust me, you need it.

Text.SourceString: The shop is closed; I'm taking a break now.
Text.LocalizedString: The shop is closed; I'm taking a break now.

Text.SourceString: Oh, do you need anything, sweetie? The bar is right there.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, do you need anything, sweetie? The bar is right there.

Text.SourceString: I'm heading home after this.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm heading home after this.

Text.SourceString: The food here isn't bad, but the drink is better.
Text.LocalizedString: The food here isn't bad, but the drink is better.
